{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/elements","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">小结</div>\n<p><strong>elements</strong> 返回一个 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormControlsCollection\"><code>HTMLFormControlsCollection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (<code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-75708506\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTMLCollection</a></code>) 其中包含 FORM 的所有控件。需要注意的是，其中不包括 <code>type</code> 等于 <code>image</code> 的 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\" title=\"input\">input</a></code> 元素。</p>\n<p>你可以通过&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API\" title=\"DOM/element.name\">name</a> 或&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/id\" title=\"DOM/element.id\">id</a>来访问对应的控件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>nodeList</em> = <em>HTMLFormElement</em>.elements\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"实例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> inputs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"form1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>elements<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> inputByIndex <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> inputs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> inputByName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> inputs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"login\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/forms.html#dom-form-elements\" title=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/forms.html#dom-form-elements\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5, Section 4.10.3, The form Element</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-76728479\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 HTML: elements</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"实例","id":"example"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"}],"summary":"elements 返回一个 HTMLFormControlsCollection (en-US) (HTMLCollection) 其中包含 FORM 的所有控件。需要注意的是，其中不包括 type 等于 image 的 input 元素。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement.elements","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/htmlformelement/elements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/htmlformelement/elements/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"}